### Shell Execute - Get .NET Version
POST http://localhost:5000/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 5,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "ShellExecuteAsync",
    "arguments": {
      "command": "dotnet",
      "arguments": ["--version"]
    }
  }
}

###

### Shell Execute - Search for .cs files with ripgrep
POST http://localhost:5000/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 6,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "ShellExecuteAsync",
    "arguments": {
      "command": "rg",
      "arguments": ["--files", "--type", "cs"]
    }
  }
}

###

### Shell Execute - List directory tree
POST http://localhost:5000/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 7,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "ShellExecuteAsync",
    "arguments": {
      "command": "tree",
      "arguments": ["-L", "2"]
    }
  }
}

